Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest queue add

Purpose:
  Create one generation task for one `.sdpub` chapter.

Usage:
  spinedigest queue add <archive.sdpub> --chapter <id> --task <reading-graph|summary> --accept-cost [--boost] [--llm <json>] [--prompt <text>]

Options:
  --chapter <id>       Required chapter id.
  --task <task>        Required task: reading-graph or summary.
  --accept-cost        Explicitly acknowledge LLM cost and wait time.
  --boost              Insert the new job at the front of the queued jobs.
  --llm <json>         Override LLM configuration for this job.
  --prompt <text>      Override extraction prompt for this job.

Examples:
  spinedigest queue add book.sdpub --chapter 3 --task reading-graph --accept-cost
  spinedigest queue add book.sdpub --chapter 3 --task summary --accept-cost --boost
